        {
            "title": "黃竹坑 深灣9號 淺調長廳簡約雅緻",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黃竹坑 深灣9號 淺調長廳簡約雅緻\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6e7b496b87133d2b5c0cefee2a875ae6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050918170494198.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黃竹坑 深灣9號 淺調長廳簡約雅緻</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>位於南區黃竹坑海景豪宅的深灣9號，毗鄰深灣遊艇會。今日為大家介紹該屋苑9座高層C室，單位實用面積595方呎，為市場罕有小複式，可享香港仔海峽海景，現時叫價1,600萬，實用呎價約26,891元。\n\n</p>\n<p>踏入放盤單位，複式下層為廳堂及廚房，複式上層則為寢室，私隱度高。當中客廳設計實用，方便住戶擺放家具。\n\n</p>\n<p>飯廳有連落地玻璃趟門連露台，可透過落地玻璃窗引入自然光，對正有深灣遊艇會及避風塘海景。飯廳旁為開放式廚房，廚房有U形廚櫃，備餐空間足夠。\n\n</p>\n<p>單位為1房設計方正實用，中間放置可三邊落牀的雙人牀，前方亦有電視，另有L形到頂衣櫃，輕鬆放置所有衣物，房間有落地大窗，外連工作平台，亦可享香港仔海峽海景，觀景開揚。浴室保養良好，有灰色雲石牆，基本潔貝齊全。\n\n</p>\n<p>深灣9號坐落惠福道上，樓齡約12年，由6座分層大廈及11間洋房組成，提供411個單位，基座設住客會所，提供室外及室內游泳池、桌球室、私人影院、健身室等。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239638/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"廁所新淨，裝修企理。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e8c2e38ff621e9c7d6226c9d10baba4/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_9_39_10_AM_4_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廁所新淨，裝修企理。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239639/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"複式上層為主人房，中間放置可三邊落牀的雙人牀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d1b7f95ec40695f5a75a4d305b009752/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_9_39_10_AM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        複式上層為主人房，中間放置可三邊落牀的雙人牀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239640/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"放盤廳及房也可享有深灣遊艇會及避風塘海景。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9623c989080834681ff3d06d07d3f12f/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_9_39_10_AM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        放盤廳及房也可享有深灣遊艇會及避風塘海景。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239642/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃竹坑深灣9號外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41d789054e9147a82a0b9be29bae8ba0/2025-05/DPPF0927MARINELLA002.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃竹坑深灣9號外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239641/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃竹坑深灣9號9座高層C室，單位實用面積595方呎，屬複式設計，現時叫價1600萬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/187f12b072d98deedd571d292140f84d/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-08_at_9_39_10_AM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃竹坑深灣9號9座高層C室，單位實用面積595方呎，屬複式設計，現時叫價1600萬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>放盤單位資料  </h2>\n<p>物業名稱：深灣9號\n\n</p>\n<p>地址：惠福道9號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：12年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：9座高層C室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：595方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：1房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫價：1600萬元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎價：26891元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：世紀21首選置業\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：9653 5468(Louie Wan)\n\n</p>\n<p>*相片由代理行提供\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068126/即時-地產-黃竹坑-深灣9號-淺調長廳簡約雅緻",
