        {
            "title": "歐霸│曼聯與熱刺上演全英決賽 英超6隊戰歐聯創歷史",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼聯與熱刺上演全英決賽，英超6隊戰歐聯創歷史。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/07dd162a5ac044ef672df0f2888ed66f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050917434840927.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼聯與熱刺上演全英決賽，英超6隊戰歐聯創歷史。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周四歐霸4強次回合，英超雙雄曼聯和熱刺，分別擊敗畢爾包及波杜基林特，擴大首回合的優勢強勢晉級，5月21日兩軍將上演全英決賽。由於紅魔和熱刺本季英超成績差勁，目前分別排15和16位，早已失去透過聯賽排名參加來季歐戰的資格，換言之兩隊的其中一隊會用歐霸冠軍的身份取得下屆歐聯席位，令英超破紀錄地有6支球隊出戰歐聯。\n\n</p><h2>全英決賽5月21日上演</h2>\n<p>熱刺今場憑射手蘇蘭基和右閘柏度樸路在下半場各入一球，作客2:0擊敗波杜基林特，兩回合計贏5:1，將與曼聯在5月21日爭冠。兩隊今季同病相鄰，彼此於英超脫腳長居積分榜下游，早已放棄聯賽，將希望放在歐霸賽事，力圖奪冠獲得下季的歐聯參賽資格，如今兩隊在決賽會師，代表這個歐聯席位已鎖定在英超球會身上。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"蘇蘭基為熱刺先開紀錄。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d60e46de589f9a72265b5395dabf0422/2025-05/1_20.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇蘭基為熱刺先開紀錄。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"蘇蘭基率先破門。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d2f7cca65a81347ab2210c858272a7c1/2025-05/2_0_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇蘭基率先破門。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"蘇蘭基近年入球頻頻。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f1b1a73037f7a9bb5bb5885124a60890/2025-05/3_19.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        蘇蘭基近年入球頻頻。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"柏度樸路的傳中，變成入球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68e162d6f412657f7801e199196aa704/2025-05/4_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        柏度樸路的傳中，變成入球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"柏度樸路為熱刺射成2:0。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a4d85f689f0d443f955aec389ffd970/2025-05/5_12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        柏度樸路為熱刺射成2:0。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺將與曼聯在歐霸決賽會師，上演全英對決。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a0bdd31f04f1cb5f0e5900d098307d0d/2025-05/174678319942250.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺將與曼聯在歐霸決賽會師，上演全英對決。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺眾將慶祝躋身歐霸決賽。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3cf73ccb3a5f518be6d7db8ad54f3813/2025-05/7_14.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺眾將慶祝躋身歐霸決賽。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺希望透過歐霸冠軍身份，出戰來季歐聯。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ed8425028216cfbd1f0045d57ea1029c/2025-05/8_8.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺希望透過歐霸冠軍身份，出戰來季歐聯。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺上下希望首奪歐霸。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/25cc53dd4a935abd548b6acd8eaf15ba/2025-05/9_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺上下希望首奪歐霸。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺(綠衫)雙殺波杜基林特入決賽。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43b5ca218d8eb4514a06fde7060fd20e/2025-05/174678331327172.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺(綠衫)雙殺波杜基林特入決賽。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>下季6支英超隊踢歐聯</h2>\n<p>由於英超隊在今季歐霸成績出眾，早已確定下季會額外獲得一個歐聯名額，由4隊變成5隊，現時再加上熱刺或曼聯，將會史無前例有6隊參加這項歐洲最頂級的球會比賽，創下歷史。而英超之前最多試過有5隊一起踢歐聯，是2017至18球季，當時曼聯、車路士、利物浦、曼城和熱刺參加，該年後4隊以聯賽前4名的身份獲得資格，紅魔就是以歐霸盟主取得席位。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯中場美臣蒙特梅開二度，領軍躋身決賽。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8aa5723ce074ee5aff28d71924e486d/2025-05/2025-05-08T205707Z_1604095809_UP1EL581M76WK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-ATH-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯中場美臣蒙特梅開二度，領軍躋身決賽。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯將與熱刺上演全英決賽。美聯社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/961cc57da9f1157c1224a8134d0c56be/2025-05/Britain_Soccer_Europa_League_66887--13329.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯將與熱刺上演全英決賽。美聯社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯中場美臣蒙特(左)梅開二度。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4326cb5c773fd3a7250ed21935b9f6f7/2025-05/2025-05-08T212418Z_1304691782_UP1EL581L4SVF_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-ATH-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯中場美臣蒙特(左)梅開二度。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯同樣希望透過歐霸冠軍的身份，取得下季歐聯席位。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/265524ac01171b6426560c7638f7db54/2025-05/10_8.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯同樣希望透過歐霸冠軍的身份，取得下季歐聯席位。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯將於5月21日與熱刺爭奪歐霸冠軍。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34d0685d0c520768287040c57cc4f4d5/2025-05/11_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯將於5月21日與熱刺爭奪歐霸冠軍。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068119/即時-體育-歐霸│曼聯與熱刺上演全英決賽-英超6隊戰歐聯創歷史",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 17:56:21",
